    • compareTo

      public int compareTo​(User rhs)
      Compare two uses according to their full name, lexicographically
      Specified by:
      compareTo in interface java.lang.Comparable<User>
      Returns:
      the value 0 if full name of parametric user is equal to this user's full name; a value greater than 0 if full name of parametric user is lexicographically less than the full name of this user; and a value less than 0 if full name of parametric user is lexicographically greater than full name of this user.
